name: Raspberry Pi Weather Station Dashboard
tagline: a graphical interface for your weather station data
body:
Raspberry Pi Weather Station Dashboard
======================================

This project will provide you with a graphical dashboard of the current weather observation based on the Raspberry Pi Weather Station data.

#### Contributing

Contributions to this project are very welcome, and can be made by using the program and providing feedback or by assisting in the programming and submitting pull requests. In either case, please read the [contributing page](https://github.com/JoshuaCarroll/Raspberry-Pi-Weather-Station-Dashboard/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) for instructions.

* [Live demo](http://n5jlc.duckdns.org/dashboard)
* [Development branch demo (may be buggy or non-functional at times)](http://n5jlc.duckdns.org/dev)
* [Code repository](https://github.com/JoshuaCarroll/Raspberry-Pi-Weather-Station-Dashboard)
